<../../../index.trig> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#5779c7e729fdbbfe5c09030fa57a986f>.
<#5779c7e729fdbbfe5c09030fa57a986f> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/REA>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-04-14T17:12:10.655Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#5779c7e729fdbbfe5c09030fa57a986f> {
<http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/REA> a <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#Concept>;
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/deprecated> "false";
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#inScheme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Europees Uitvoerend Agentschap onderzoek"@nl, "Eiropas Pētniecības izpildaģentūra"@lv, "Európai Kutatási Végrehajtó Ügynökség"@hu, "Europos mokslinių tyrimų vykdomoji įstaiga"@lt, "An Ghníomhaireacht Feidhmiúcháin Eorpach um Thaighde"@ga, "Europejska Agencja Wykonawcza ds. Badań Naukowych"@pl, "Det Europæiske Forvaltningsorgan for Forskning"@da, "Europska izvršna agencija za istraživanje"@hr, "L-Aġenzija Eżekuttiva Ewropea għar-Riċerka"@mt, "Agência de Execução Europeia da Investigação"@pt, "European Research Executive Agency"@en, "Európska výkonná agentúra pre výskum"@sk, "Europäische Exekutivagentur für die Forschung"@de, "Европейска изпълнителна агенция за научни изследвания"@bg, "Evropská výkonná agentura pro výzkum"@cs, "Agenția Executivă Europeană pentru Cercetare"@ro, "Europeiska genomförandeorganet för forskning"@sv, "Agence exécutive européenne pour la recherche"@fr, "Euroopa Teadusuuringute Rakendusamet"@et, "Agencia Ejecutiva Europea de Investigación"@es, "Agenzia esecutiva europea per la ricerca"@it, "Ευρωπαϊκός Εκτελεστικός Οργανισμός Έρευνας"@el, "Euroopan tutkimuksen toimeenpanovirasto"@fi, "Evropska izvajalska agencija za raziskave"@sl;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The European Research Executive Agency is entrusted with the implementation of the following (parts of) Union programmes: Horizon Europe: Pillar I: Marie Skłodowska-Curie Actions (MSCA) and Research Infrastructures; Horizon Europe: Pillar II, Cluster 2: Culture, Creativity and Inclusive Society; Cluster 3: Civil Security for Society; and Cluster 6: Food, Bio-economy, Natural Resources, Agriculture and Environment; Horizon Europe: Part ‘Widening participation and strengthening the European Research Area’: ‘Spreading excellence and widening participation’; ‘Reforming and enhancing the European R&I System’; Information provision and promotion measures concerning agricultural products; Research Programme of the Research Fund for Coal and Steel. Moreover, the European Research Executive Agency shall be responsible for general administrative and logistical support services, in particular: Central Validation Service (SEDIA); call planning for all programmes and services participating in eGrants; expert management, as well as with the implementation of the legacy of the following (parts of) Union programmes: Horizon 2020: Part I: Marie Skłodowska-Curie Actions and Research Infrastructures; Horizon 2020: Part III: Societal Challenge 2: Food security, sustainable agriculture and forestry, marine, maritime and inland water research and the bio-economy; Societal Challenge 5: Climate action, Environment, resource efficiency and raw materials; Societal Challenge 6: Europe in a changing world-Inclusive, innovative and reflective societies; Societal Challenge 7: Secure Societies-Protecting freedom and security of Europe and its citizens; Horizon 2020: Part IV: Spreading excellence and widening participation; Horizon 2020: Part V: Science with and for society; FP7: actions ‘Research for SMEs’ and ‘Research for SME associations of the Specific Programme Capacities’; FP7: the theme ‘Security’ of the specific programme cooperation of the Seventh Framework Programme; FP7 Specific Programme People; Information provision and promotion measures concerning agricultural products; Research Programme of the Research Fund for Coal and Steel."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "10.2848"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#DOI_P>, "REA"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>, "JW"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#OP_CAT>, "REA_1"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#PUB_CORP>, "95234"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#ISBN_RG>, "REA_CRF_232513"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#WHOISWHO>, "REA"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>, "COB0001633"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>, "REA"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#WHOISWHO>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "REA"@da, "REA"@bg, "REA"@en, "REA"@et, "REA"@nl, "REA"@hu, "REA"@el, "REA"@lv, "REA"@it, "REA"@sv, "REA"@mt, "REA"@fi, "REA"@cs, "REA"@pl, "REA"@lt, "REA"@hr, "REA"@de, "REA"@es, "REA"@sk, "REA"@pt, "REA"@ro, "REA"@ga, "REA"@fr, "REA"@sl;
    <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#sameAs> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/REA_2021_0>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/identifier> "REA";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/op-code> "REA";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/op-code> "REA";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/start.use> "2021-04-01";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/authority-code> "REA";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/op-mapped-code> _:b1955_b1954_b1953_df_15_568, _:b1955_b1954_b1953_df_15_569, _:b1955_b1954_b1953_df_15_570;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#broader> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/COM>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#historyNote> "According to the Commission Implementing Decision (EU) 2021/173 of 12 February 2021 (http://data.europa.eu/eli/dec_impl/2021/173/oj), the European Research Executive Agency is established from 1 April 2021 until 31 December 2028 and it succeeds and replaces the Research Executive Agency."@en.
